Package com.bot.worker.common.events

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AppInitEvent
    Event which requests component initialization
    GetStatusRequest
    Requests STATUS info for given task or all tasks
    GetStatusResponse
    Response on GetStatusRequest
    GetStatusResponse.TaskInfo  
    TaskConfigLoadedResponse
    Response on TaskConfigReloadRequest
    TaskConfigReloadRequest
    Request to RELOAD task configuration from config file
    TaskDropRequest
    Request to cancel task and remove all information from app
    TaskHoldRequest
    Request to cancel task execution
    TaskScheduleRequest
    Request to SCHEDULE task
    TaskUpdateRequest
    Ancestor for all events which request task(s) update
    TaskUpdateResponse
    Task update request processing result.
